description: Enjoy axe throwing without risking any damage to you, or your surroundings. Stick the Outside Inside’s Axe Throwing target to the side of your adventure van or tent and let the foam hatchets fly.Hook and loop sticks axes where thrown.Includes 4 foam axes (23 x 15cm), a 68cm log style target and a storage pouch.
name: Outside Inside Travel Toy Axe Throwing Game
